snippet.title: Paramount Entertainment Australia
snippet.description: Welcome to the official Paramount Entertainment Australia YouTube channel! Paramount Pictures is a global entertainment company that creates and distributes quality movies, television programming and digital content, from premium brands including: Paramount Pictures, Paramount TV, CBS, Showtime, Miramax, Nickelodeon and MTV. Watch on your device - anywhere.
